UID:event_313640984@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260310T023729Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260310T181500
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260310T203000
SUMMARY:Trivia at Trailhead (Novato)
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\n🎉 Join Us for Trivia Night! 🧠☕
 ️\nThis event is cross-posted with Sonoma Marin Brat Pack\, Marin County
  Millennials\, and North Bay 20s30s Meetup\, so RSVPs may not reflect the 
 full crowd.\n\nWe’re Team Quizzards! I’ll be at most events\, and if I
  can’t make it\, you’ll still find some friendly regulars there. Look 
 for us at the back of the coffee shop — come say hi and join the fun! 
 🎉\n\n🕡 Trivia kicks off promptly at 6:30 PM\, so swing by a bit earl
 ier if you'd like to grab a drink or something tasty to eat before we get 
 started. I plan to be there at 6 pm to try to get us a good table .\n📍 
 Location:\nTrailhead Coffee\n127 San Marin Drive\, Novato\, CA\nBring your
  friends\, your appetite\, and your A-game — see you there! 🙌
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-marin-brat-pack/events/3136409
 84/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260305T001853Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260305T001853Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313604851@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260310T023729Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260311T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260311T213000
SUMMARY:Redwood Nights - Storytelling Under the Stars @ Deer Park Village 
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nJoin in for an evening of storytelling
  done under the magical starlit canopy of the Redwoods. This week's theme 
 is "The Moment I finally Chose Myself..."\n\nStories are sometimes poignan
 t\, sometimes hilarious and always true. Featuring storytellers that have 
 appeared on HBO\, PBS\, NPR\, MOTH & more. Complimentary hors d'ouvers and
  the venue has full bar plus additional wine & beer bar.\n\nEarly Bird tic
 kets are $35 and can be purchased at link below:\n\nhttps://redwoodnightsl
 ive.com/storytelling-under-the-stars/\n\nI'll plan to get early to grab se
 ats and we can introduce ourselves before show starts
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-marin-brat-pack/events/3136048
 51/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260302T174604Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260302T174604Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313675364@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260310T023729Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260311T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260311T220000
SUMMARY:Karaoke Contest
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\n🎤 Mac’s Karaoke Contest 2026\nMac
 ’s is hosting a karaoke contest\, and you can register for free on Event
 brite using the link below. If you plan to actually enter the contest\, I 
 recommend arriving early to make sure your name gets on the list.\nI’m p
 lanning to stop by just to observe and enjoy the local talent. Should be a
  fun night!\nThere are multiple dates scheduled\, so if you can’t make t
 he first one\, the contest will continue over the next few weeks - so be s
 ure to enter the correct date.\nRegister here:\nhttps://www.eventbrite.com
 /e/macs-karaoke-contest-2026-tickets-1984093772885?aff=ebdssbdestsearch
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-marin-brat-pack/events/3136753
 64/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260307T013651Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260307T013651Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
