DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T223000
SUMMARY:Joose at the Mystic on 3/14
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nIf the raw emotion and dynamic energy 
 of bands like Nirvana\, Pearl Jam\, Smashing Pumpkins\, Foo Fighters\, and
  other pop-rock classics from the 90s are your jam\, then this where you n
 eed to be.\n\nHead on out to the Mystic in Petaluma for a night of making 
 new friends & great music.\n\nThis event probably sell out so buy tickets 
 as soon as you can. See you there\n\nhttps://muhfugginjoose.com/
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/sonoma-marin-brat-pack/events/3133622
 99/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260215T014134Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260215T014134Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
